          We deploy the same AI ads system for clients — brief in, campaign out,
          production-ready creatives in under a working day.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/#products"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-white text-brand-black text-[13px] font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-brand-cream transition-colors duration-200"
        >
          See how it works
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none">
            <path d="M1 7h12M8 2l5 5-5 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Credits footer -->
    <div class="border-t border-white/6 px-6 py-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-8 gap-y-2 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-white/20">
        <span>Creative Director · Claude AI</span>
        <span>Director of Photography · GPT Image-2</span>
        <span>Art Direction · Purist Studio</span>
        <span>Production · n8n + Claude Skills</span>
        <span>Copy · Claude AI</span>
      </div>
    </div>

